clause.text:
mechanisms are in place to ensure that
				progress toward water quality goals for the Chesapeake Bay ecosystem are
				achieved;

the allocation of funds reflects each
				Chesapeake Bay State’s responsibility and contribution towards achieving water
				quality goals;

subparagraph.text:
